        <headline>Heat Advisory issued August 12 at 2:55AM PDT until August 12 at 8:00PM PDT by NWS Spokane WA</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Hot temperatures in the 90s on the Camas Prairie and near
100 in Kamiah.

* WHERE...Nezperce, Winchester, Kamiah, Soldiers Meadow Road, and
Craigmont.

* WHEN...Until 8 PM PDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures will increase the risk of heat-related
illnesses, especially for those without effective cooling or
adequate hydration.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
